Hi All,

Here is my proposal.

We can use shopify Line Item Properties for this purpose ( with some customization in cart.liquid ).

please refer the following screen shot



If quantity is e.g 5 for a single product, than we need to show them 5 rows of text box ( can be achieved with java script ).

So the steps will be

1) Customer checkout.

2) Order creation in Shopify along with these Custom Line Item Properties.

3) Register Order creation Webhook for our custom Module.

4) Our custom module will get a complete Order object along with Line Item Properties.

5) Using LearnUpon API we can create as much as user we want and enrol them.


What we need.

1) Admin Access ( with theme editing and creating web hook capability ) for http://247training.solutions

2) Server with cpanel access ( to host custom php module )

3) LearnUpon API access


Time Estimation

1) cart page customization - 8 hours

2) PHP module - 24 hours

( that includes design, dev, deploy and unit test )
